trans-unit.source: Specifies an algorithm to hash all files in an assembly.
trans-unit.target: Angir en algoritme hashe alle filene i en samling.

trans-unit.source: The file hash values and names in the assembly are stored in the assembly manifest.
trans-unit.target: Filen nummerverdier og navn i samlingen er lagret i samlingsmanifestet.

trans-unit.source: When a file is loaded, the hash value is used to verify that a file has not been changed since the manifest was built.
trans-unit.target: N책r en fil er lastet inn, brukes hash-verdien til 책 bekrefte at en fil ikke har blitt endret siden manifestet ble bygd.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Reflection.AssemblyAlgorithmIdAttribute"></xref> class with the specified hash algorithm, using one of the members of <xref href="System.Configuration.Assemblies.AssemblyHashAlgorithm"></xref> to represent the hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Reflection.AssemblyAlgorithmIdAttribute"> </xref> klassen med den angitte nummeralgoritmen for medlemmer av <xref href="System.Configuration.Assemblies.AssemblyHashAlgorithm"> </xref> til 책 representere hash-algoritmen.

trans-unit.source: A member of <xref uid="langword_csharp_AssemblyHashAlgorithm" name="AssemblyHashAlgorithm" href=""></xref> that represents the hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Et medlem av <xref uid="langword_csharp_AssemblyHashAlgorithm" name="AssemblyHashAlgorithm" href=""> </xref> som representerer hash-algoritmen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Reflection.AssemblyAlgorithmIdAttribute"></xref> class with the specified hash algorithm, using an unsigned integer to represent the hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Reflection.AssemblyAlgorithmIdAttribute"> </xref> klassen med den angitte nummeralgoritmen, ved hjelp av et heltall uten fortegn til 책 representere hash-algoritmen.

trans-unit.source: An unsigned integer representing the hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Et heltall uten fortegn som representerer hash-algoritmen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the hash algorithm of an assembly manifest's contents.
trans-unit.target: Henter nummeralgoritmen med et samlingsmanifest innhold.

trans-unit.source: An unsigned integer representing the assembly hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Et heltall uten fortegn som representerer samlingen hash-algoritmen.
